  <bioghist id="aspace_4403b8f38dbbb4a6b441a00001d09dcb">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>The Sunnyside Gardens Preservation Alliance is a neighborhood organization "dedicated to the preservation and revitalization of the Sunnyside Gardens National Register Historic District." The Sunnyside Gardens Oral History Program was funded by the Clarence Stein Institute at Cornell University. Tony Rohling serves as the Program Director and Herbert Reynolds as the Historian.</p>  </bioghist>
